ItemCommentInput is a BusinessClass
    owned by ic
    prefix is W7730

    Ontology
    	symbolic key is ItemCommentInput
    
    Patterns
        implements StaticJava
        disable AuditIndex
		disable Auditing 
       	disable EffectiveDated
       	disable DataTranslations
    
    Persistent Fields
        RunGroup
        ItemGroup               
        Item                    is like Item
        InterfacedItem          is Alpha 32
        Comment                 
        BeginDate               is Date
        EndDate                 is Date
        ItemCommentType
		
    Sets

        ByRunGroup
			Sort Order
				RunGroup
				ItemGroup
				InterfacedItem
				Item
				ItemCommentInput
		
    Actions

        Create is a Create Action

        Update is an Update Action
        
        Delete is a Delete Action
        
        InterfaceItemCommentInformation is a Set Action
			Parameters
				PrmRunGroup              is AlphaUpper 30
				PrmItemGroup             is an ItemGroup
			
			Sort Order
				RunGroup
				ItemGroup
			
			Instance Selection
				where  (RunGroup	= PrmRunGroup
				and     ItemGroup   = PrmItemGroup)  
				
			Action Rules
			
				RunGroup Set Rules
					Exit Rules
						
						invoke CreateItemInformation ItemInformationWorksheet
							invoked.PrmItemGroup    = PrmItemGroup
							invoked.PrmRunGroup     = PrmRunGroup
				
				Instance Rules
				
					invoke CreateItemWorksheetFromCSV ItemInformationWorksheet
						fill in fields from this instance
						invoked.FinalItemNumber     													= Item
						invoked.ItemCommentNew.ItemCommentOccurs.ItemCommentDetails[1].Comment			= Comment
						invoked.ItemCommentNew.ItemCommentOccurs.ItemCommentDetails[1].BeginDate        = BeginDate
						invoked.ItemCommentNew.ItemCommentOccurs.ItemCommentDetails[1].EndDate          = EndDate
						invoked.ItemCommentNew.ItemCommentOccurs.ItemCommentDetails[1].ItemCommentType  = ItemCommentType

       				invoke Delete
